'''Premanand Shantaram Ramani zaka Dr. P. S. Ramani nanvan vollkhotat,to ek Bharoti Goenchea rajiacho nervam piddecho voiz  zavn asa, Taka tachea Newcaste hantuntlea vavrak ani tachea nervam piddechea xostrkriechea kuxolltaiek-Flip Ramani kuxolltai ani PLIF lagun vollkhotat. Sodheak Mumboichea  Lilavati Hospitalantlo to jiextt nervam patti-konneacho sorjon asa<sup>[1]</sup> Ek vorsavollicho lamb pol’leanchi dhanvddi tachea manak Goeant korpant ieta zaka Dr P S Ramani Goa Marathon" nanv dilam.<sup>[2][3]</sup>''' 

== Adlem Jivit ==
Ramani eka  Goenchea Wadi Talaulim ganvant zolmolo ani vaddlo. Ek khalche orthik fattbhuincher aslolean, to  Fonddenchea A.J de Almeida  iskolak savn io-voch dor disa cholon kortalo,Mon lavn kam korun, to iskolant poilo ietalo ani rajiant to dusro ailolo asa,  Tannem gonnitant  100%  gunn melloileat donui  SSC porikxent toxench ontor-vinean porikxent.Punn, tannem voiz zavpak chintlem ani taka Mumboi Vixv vidheapitthachi xixhovruti favo zali, Tannem nervam piddent khaxeleponn ghetlam..<sup>[4]</sup> 

== Karkird ==
Newcastle upon Tyne hanchea nagrikanchea iesiesponni ilaz kela dekhun Ramanik ontorraxttrio fank mell’lli. Thoim zaitea lokak fattichem ani fattikonnache thoinchea kollxeachea khonnink lagun. prosong asle Hi fank ani bhovman mell’llolo astanai, to Bharotant portolo..<sup>[4]</sup>

1974 vorsa , taka  Goa Medical College patthovpant ailo, zoim tachea agllea-vegllea vavrak lagun taka tachea ghorchea rajeant xroi favo zalem..<sup>[4]</sup>


















Voizuki bondhutvant, Ramanik namna tachea nove manddavollik ani kuxolltaiek nervam piddent asa.Tachi chodd famad kuxolltai disc kaddpant asa zaka ."Flip Ramani Technique" mhonn vollkhopant ieta.<sup>[1]</sup>  1973 vorsa , tannem  PLIF manddnni kaddli zaka Posterior Lumbar Interbod ji spondylolysis ani spndylolisthesis ilaz korpant vaporpant ieta  .<sup>[5]</sup>

LTM Medical College hichea Nervam pidde vibhagacho Professor ani Mukheli koso to tosoch Mumboichea Tata Memorial Hospital Oncological Neuro-Spinal Surgeon,  bospagari zala.To  Association of Neuro-Spinal Surgeons of India hacho iezman ani Neuro-trauma Society of India hacho iezman aslo.<sup>[6][7]</sup>

Sodheak to nervam piddecho xostrio korpi ani jiextt nervam fatti konnacho xostr kria korpi koso Lilavati Hospital, Mumboi hanga vavurta .<sup>[1]</sup> Tannem 2001 vorsa fattikonneachi xostrkria  kelea famad Sarika nottiechi ji adli ghorkan’n  ani tosripam jikhpi kolakar ani digdorspi Kamal Hassanachi asa..<sup>[8]</sup> Tannem Goenkar nattkist, kovi ani rajkornni Vishnu Wagh hancho 2016 vorsa ilaz kela..<sup>[9]</sup>

