=== '''Poropkar''' ===
Aplea ganvam khatir kitem tori korunk utsuk aslolean, tannem aplem purvozanchem ghor moddlam jem 1926 vorsa bandlolem, ani ek malliechem ghor bandlam zantunt 10000 pustokanchi vachnaloi, 2000 khellnni, bhurgeank ek khellpachi bag ani 200 lokank bospacho ek vosro hancho aspav asa..Tannem ek adhunik veaomxalla hea zagear bandlea ani heo sovloti bhousa khatir funkott vo ek nanvam purtea rok’komank bhettoileat.  Tannem ek khellacho zago komunidadichea zagear vistarit kela..<sup>[4]</sup>

Ramani ek krikett khellachi spordha  praiojit korta ani "Dr P S Ramani Goa Marathon" hantunt to kriaxil asa jichi manddavoll Ahilyabai Ramani Pratishtan korta ji sonstha tannem sthapit kelea.,<sup>[2]</sup> Hea kariavollik sonvsar bhor lokachem akorxon asa;.<sup>[10]</sup> Ramani he ghoddnnechi sondi tornnatteank kriaxil zavnk ut’tejon dita ani tankam koslei piraiechi ott nastana kosrotechem mhotv xikoita.<sup>[11][12]</sup> 

== Tosripam ani Proxonsa ==
Newcastle hantuntlea kamank lagun, Dr Ramanki Research Man of the Year award Englandant favo zalam. University of Chicago hacho protistthit Paul Bucy Award mellovpak Asiantlo to poilo zavn asa. 2011 vorsa, taka British Association of Spinal Surgeons hannim lifetime achievement award, bhettoilam ani Hungary desant tachea bhovmanak ek ttopal tikett kaddlea.<sup>[13][5]</sup> Rokhddench, eka  Cirebon, Indonesiachea hospitalan, ek xostria korpi  theatre blockak tachem nanv dilam, Ganvghora, tachea ganvchea lokamni tachea poropkar lagun eka ganvchea rosteak tachem nanv dilam..<sup>[4]</sup>

